<br>
I was thinking that, amongst the three tanking classes, the Warrior is the only one without an innate unique timer based skill.<br>
<br>
The SK has HT, and the Paladin LH.<br>
<br>
The Warrior also doesn't have any special gifts (short of AA) analgous with the spell aggro that the SK and Paladin have at their disposal.<br>
<br>
I suggest that Warriors, be given, at level 1, a unique Hate Generating skill, akin to HT and LH.<br>
<br>
It would be on a timer (9,18,30?) seconds, and generate an amount of hate computed like HT or LH (not exactly) but based on level of the Warrior.<br>
<br>
This amount could be tweaked to not be overbalanced.<br>
<br>
This ability would compliment Taunt, not replace it, as the other Tanks have taunt too, but Warriors need something to innate to compete with Spell Aggro.<br>
<br>
This will help Warriors of all levels do their job, without relying on gimmicks.<br>
<br>
As to what this skill, I don't know, Infuriate, or maybe something involving the Warriors innately supperior supposed study of Warfare.<br>
<br>
Any thoughts? <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~carriedingus/lionfist.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=torqe>Torqe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 61<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/12/03 7:55:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3013.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Idea for Hate Generating Skill...</span><hr size=1> personally, i dont have a problem getting/maintaining agro unless a pally chain stuns... But as for the idea. it would prolly be on the same timer as there HT/LoH but if so i would imagine a HUGE amount of agro.<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.fortunecity.com/orange99//sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderpictures/dragonball477.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
