<br>
(Level x 5) + 50 added to the Hate List, usable at 200 range, on separate 3 min timer.<br>
<br>
Hell, I'd even say hang it off the /shield timer.  You have a choice, /shield someone or /Insult the mob.This scales to be 55 - 375 Hate usable at a 200 range every 3 min.  Nothing overly powerful by ANY stretch, and personally, I'd see it as an answer to the warrior early-agro problem. <p>Barja Bardagi<br>
