<br>
As it stands warriors have a unique niche tanking heavy damage mobs, we're not supposed to be the best at tanking EVERY type of mob. Furthermore, with decent weapons, agro really isn't an issue after the first few seconds. If warriors had this ability there'd be no reason for a shadowknight/paladin to exist.<br>
<br>
Some of you guys have to realize that hybrids have a new role as tanks for low dps mobs whom slow/agro debuff etc. We're the best at tanking mobs ie: physically taking damage, its not reasonable for us to be the best at every aspect of tanking.<br>
